high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the microwave.
Pick up the egg to the right of the microwave.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Place the egg in the garbage bin to the left of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg in a trash bin.

high_descs: Turn right to cross the kitchen and just before you get to the stove, turn left and continue to the dishwasher.
Pick up the egg from beside the microwave.
Move a step to the left to stand directly in front of the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Carry the egg just a bit to the left so you're closer to the trash bin between the fridge and counter.
Place the egg in the trash bin.
Turn right and walk to the counter on the left with the white dishwasher.
Pick up the egg to the right of the microwave on the shelf above the counter.
Turn left and look up at the microwave on the shelf.
Put the egg inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, walk to the right and turn right to face the gray bin on the floor.
Put the heated egg inside the gray bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg in a bin.
